overview.en: QOS aims to build a 'next generation enterprise-level application community' by building a blockchain based operating system, a unified identity authentication system, a self-motivated double-layer token protocol, and a double-layer mining mechanism for 'super-node + transaction mining'
overview.zh: QOS通过搭建公链与联盟链混合的底层操作系统、统一身份认证体系、自激励的双层代币协议、超级节点+交易挖矿的双层挖矿机制，目标是建设“下一代企业级应用社区”
